    <entry>
      <title>matlab中的面向对象编程</title>
      <link href="/2024/07/03/matlab%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%A2%E5%90%91%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B/"/>
      <url>/2024/07/03/matlab%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%A2%E5%90%91%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="MATLAB-面向对象编程语法"><a href="#MATLAB-面向对象编程语法" class="headerlink" title="MATLAB 面向对象编程语法"></a>MATLAB 面向对象编程语法</h1><h2 id="面向对象的方法学："><a href="#面向对象的方法学：" class="headerlink" title="面向对象的方法学："></a>面向对象的方法学：</h2><p>关于类，有个直观的表述：</p><blockquote><ul><li><p>类（class）</p><p>-对现实的抽象</p><p>-属性（数据）</p><p>-方法（行为）</p></li></ul></blockquote><blockquote><ul><li><p>对象（object）</p><p>-类的具体例子</p><p>-实例</p></li></ul></blockquote><h3 id="最简单的类的构建："><a href="#最简单的类的构建：" class="headerlink" title="最简单的类的构建："></a>最简单的类的构建：</h3><figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">classdef</span> target  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">properties</span></span><br><span class="line">AoA</span><br><span class="line">range</span><br><span class="line">signal</span><br><span class="line">Aoa</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">end</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">methods</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">newtarget</span> = <span class="title">target</span><span class="params">(AoA,range,signal)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> nargin == <span class="number">3</span></span><br><span class="line">newtarget.AoA = AoA;</span><br><span class="line">newtarget.range = range;</span><br><span class="line">newtarget.signal = signal;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">end</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">end</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">identify</span><span class="params">(thistarget)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">disp</span>([<span class="string">&#x27;i am a friend,please don&#x27;&#x27;t shoot.i am at &#x27;</span> num2str(thistarget.AoA)]);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">end</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ballon = target; <span class="comment">%ballon是target类的一个实例</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>回顾：如何判断一个量是什么类型：</p><figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">% 方法一</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; isa(ballon,<span class="string">&#x27;target&#x27;</span>); <span class="comment">%target是一个类</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">ans</span> = </span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">%方法二</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; class(ballon);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">ans</span> = </span><br><span class="line">target</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>声明：只是个人学习使用，并不是教程，大家可以查看下述视频学习</p><p>视频参考:<a href="https://ww2.mathworks.cn/videos/object-oriented-programming-in-matlab-82522.html">MATLAB 面向对象编程 - MATLAB (mathworks.cn)</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
